               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā “Book of the Christening” (fols. 11ra-36vb)&#xD; II)
                     Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 36vb-105vb), incomplete&#xD;
                     - Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols.
                     45rb-52rb) &#xD; - Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols.
                     60va-65ra)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-4.</summary>
